          σ
          
            −
            3
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle p=878.5\,\varepsilon \sigma ^{-3}}
  , passes through a temperature maximum at approximately 
  
    
      
        T
        =
        0.4
        
        ε
        
          k
          
            
              B
            
          
          
            −
            1
          
        
      
    
